{{Infobox royalty
| title        = [[King of Wa]]
| predecessor  = [[Chin of Wa]]
| successor    = [[Kō of Wa|Ko of Wa]]
| issue        = [[Kō of Wa|Ko of Wa]], [[Bu of Wa]]
